text: The movie Kill Your Darlings is a 2013 historic drama set in 1944. The cast includes Daniel Radcliffe as Allen Ginsberg, Jennifer Jason Leigh as Naomi and Kyra Sedgwick as Marian Carr. This movie got very positive reviews from the critics. Category:2013 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:English-language movies Category:American independent movies
title: Kill Your Darlings
